deprecated drivers in xorg-server-21.1.0 due to the remove of (see meson.build in xorg-randac-meson.diff between the 2 releases)
- BT.h
- IBM.h
- xf86RamDac.h
non building drivers:
- glint failure due to xf86RamDac.h removal
- s3 failure due to IBM.h removal
- tga failure due to BT.h removal
- trident failure due to xf86RamDac.h removal

- nouveau can be built with a git version from the driver
- ati can be built with a git version from the driver
